客户端，支持即将发布的Quarkus 3.0 GA版本。其他值得注意的变更包括：修复msgType属性未能被正确序列化；支持enum数组；依赖项升级到quarkiverse-parent 12和javaparser-core 3.24.9。</p><p></p><h4>Apache软件基金会</h4><p></p><p></p><p>Apache软件基金会<a href=\"https://www.mail-archive.com/announce@apache.org/msg07843.html?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">发布</a>\"了CVE-2022-45143（<a href=\"https://www.rapid7.com/db/vulnerabilities/apache-tomcat-cve-2022-45143/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">Apache Tomcat JsonErrorReportValve注入</a>\"漏洞），<a href=\"https://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-10.0-doc/api/org/apache/catalina/valves/JsonErrorReportValve.html?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">JsonErrorReportValue</a>\"类不能正确转义类型、消息或描述值。这可能会导致用户提供使JSON输出无效或被操纵的值。建议开发人员将Apache Tomcat升级到10.1.2、9.0.69和8.5.84。</p><p></p><p><a href=\"https://james.apache.org/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">Apache James</a>\" 3.7.3版本<a href=\"https://www.mail-archive.com/announce@apache.org/msg07849.html?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3ND