oidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">补丁版本</a>\"，包含了一些错误修复和改进，例如：@XmlAttributes注解应该只能是String或Enum类型；限制了异步处理的事件数量，性能得到了提升；将基类移到一个新的camel-console-support模块中，避免在组件已支持控制台时默认启用控制台。Spring Boot 2.7.7的依赖项也进行了升级。关于这个版本的更多细节可以在<a href=\"https://camel.apache.org/releases/release-3.20.1/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">发布说明</a>\"中找到。</p><p></p><p>在2022年5月获得<a href=\"https://www.tomitribe.com/blog/apache-tomee-jakarta-ee-certified-after-10-years/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">Jakarta 9.1认证</a>\"后，Apache TomEE团队<a href=\"https://www.tomitribe.com/blog/apache-tomee-microprofile-5-0-certified/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">宣布</a>\"其应用服务器现在是MicroProfile 5.0的兼容实现。Tomitribe工程总监<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/jlmonteiro/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">Jean-Louis Monteiro</a>\"介绍了这一最新成就的历程，并计划支持MicroProfile 6.0和Jakarta EE 10。</p><p></p><p>MyFaces Core 4.0.0的<a href=\"https://www.mail-archive.com/announce@apache.org/msg07844.html?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">第三个候选版本</a>\"带来了一些改进，例如：为<a href=\"https://javadoc.io/static/org.apache.myfaces.core/myfaces-api/3.0.2/jakarta/faces/flow/FlowScoped.html?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">@FlowScoped</a>\"和<a href=\"https://javadoc.io/static/org.apache.myfaces.core/myfaces-api/3.0.2/jakarta/faces/view/ViewScoped.html?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">@ViewScoped</a>\"实现了CDI注解@Initialized、 @BeforeDestroyed和@Destroyed；Facelet和编程式访问的隐式对象必须使用CDI进行解析，他们因此对其表达式语言解析器进行了重构和改进。关于这个版本的更多细节可以在<a href=\"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10600&amp;version=12352404&amp;accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">发布说明</a>\"中找到。</p><p></p><h4>JetBrains</h4><p></p><p></p><p>JetBrains<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JetBrainsKtor/status/1610609857345863682?cxt=HHwWhIC-rbjIhNosAAAA&amp;accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">发布</a>\"了用于创建微服务和Web应用程序的异步框架<a href=\"https://ktor.io/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">Ktor</a>\" 2.2.2，包括了这些改进：引擎关闭时间段和超时时间现在是可配置的；swaggerUI()方法不再有太多限制，现在可以在路由内部调用；可以在<a href=\"https://javadoc.io/static/io.ktor/ktor-client-core-jvm/1.1.5/io/ktor/client/utils/CacheControl.html?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">CacheControl</a>\"类中指定immutable选项。关于这个版本的更多细节可以在<a href=\"https://ktor.io/changelog/2.2/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">变更日志</a>\"中找到。</p><p></p><h4>JHipster</h4><p></p><p></p><p>JHipster Lite 0.25.0已经<a href=\"https://github.com/jhipster/jhipster-lite/releases/tag/v0.25.0?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">发布</a>\"，包含了一些问题修复和增强，例如：支持Gradle Build Tool模块；针对Angular的一个新的inject()函数；在Maven模块中声明性地添加测试依赖项；UI按钮的改进。</p><p></p><h4>JobRunr</h4><p></p><p></p><p><a href=\"https://www.jobrunr.io/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">JobRunr</a>\" 5.3.3已经<a href=\"https://github.com/jobrunr/jobrunr/releases/tag/v5.3.3?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">发布</a>\"，修复了一个错误：附加在日志文件末尾的日志元数据键只有两个数字导致作业历史记录变得很长，日志将被删除。</p><p></p><h4>SourceBuddy</h4><p></p><p></p><p>在向Java社区引入不到一个月之后，<a href=\"https://github.com/sourcebuddy/sourcebuddy/blob/main/README.adoc?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">SourceBuddy</a>\"（可以编译在Java应用程序中动态创建的Java源代码）发布了<a href=\"https://github.com/sourcebuddy/sourcebuddy/releases/tag/2.1.0?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">2.1.0版本</a>\"，支持创建内部类和接口。InfoQ将报道更多有关SourceBuddy的新闻。</p><p></p><h4>CircleCI</h4><p></p><p></p><p>CircleCI（一家CI/CD平台公司）<a href=\"https://circleci.com/blog/january-4-2023-security-alert/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">发布</a>\"了一个安全警告。虽然他们确信在他们的系统中没有未经授权的行为，但为谨慎起见，他们建议开发人员轮换CircleCI应用程序中的密钥。CircleCI也一直在为他们的客户轮换GitHub OAuth令牌。</p><p></p><p>原文链接：</p><p><a href=\"https://www.infoq.com/news/2023/01/java-news-roundup-jan02-2023/?accessToken=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6ImRlZmF1bHQiLCJ0eXAiOiJKV1QifQ.eyJleHAiOjE2NzQwOTIyNjIsImZpbGVHVUlEIjoiZEZlMDdjblRiVU1mb0VLMCIsImlhdCI6MTY3NDA5MTk2MiwiaXNzIjoidXBsb2FkZXJfYWNjZXNzX3Jlc291cmNlIiwidXNlcklkIjo2MjMyOH0.0ChunZhjBsvrpxJ0iaY-lau2lqlVDpG5Pa22erVIbWc\">https://www.infoq.com/news/2023/01/java-news-roundup-jan02-2023/</a>\"</p><p></p><p>相关阅读：</p><p><a href=\"https://www.infoq.cn/article/pMNHAXyOfYUYFHSNFtMW\">Java 近期新闻：Jakarta Data 首版发布、Micronaut 3.8、JReleaser 1.4、Gradle 8.0-RC1</a>\"</p><p><a href=\"https://www.infoq.cn/article/5GyCp1rm0IyPIfRoDyjQ\">Spring Batch 5.0 发布，使用 JDK 17 作为基线版本并支持原生 Java</a>\"</p>",
